descriptions.see_description: In the input, you should see...colored blocks with singular outstanding blocks in the frame.
descriptions.grid_description: The output grid size...is the same
descriptions.do_description: To make the output, you have to...take the outstanding colored block, move it to outside the frame and continue the single line to edge. fill in frame with color of frame.

descriptions.see_description: In the input, you should see.... pattern of colored squares with a random colored square outside of the square
descriptions.grid_description: The output grid size...is the same as the input size
descriptions.do_description: To make the output, you have to...take the color of the random square outside the block and fill in a straight line to the border with that color on both sides. Go back in and color the random square to match the background it's on.
